Package com.smartsheet.api.internal.json

Class JacksonJsonSerializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.smartsheet.api.internal.json.JacksonJsonSerializer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JsonSerializer
    public class JacksonJsonSerializer
extends java.lang.Object
implements JsonSerializer
    This is the Jackson based JsonSerializer implementation. Thread Safety: This class is thread safe because it is immutable and the underlying Jackson ObjectMapper is thread safe as long as it is not re-configured.
